Text-Mining version 0.0.7

Perl Tools for Text Mining can either be used via a shell with TM specific 
commands or in your own perl scripts.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

Scripts must be copied somewhere reasonable.

DEPENDENCIES

 Test::More
 version
 Class::Std
 Class::Std::Utils
 YAML
 Carp
 LWP::Simple
 Time::HiRes
 DBIx::MySperqlOO
 File::Spec

